{"tid":689418,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《Batman: Arkham》系列開發商Rocksteady超人遊戲或於E3亮相！","createTime":"2018-06-04T05:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T12:23:09.000Z","uid":60286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7e38773e91b9ed0555e3cd5e5d986c64780d02","tid":689418,"uid":60286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:23:43.000Z","msg":"自從Rocksteady Studios打造了《Batman Arkham》系列後，就有傳言稱，這家遊戲開發商正在製作一個絕密的DC項目，許多人都猜測該作將基於超人或正義聯盟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/132155_772dbf44aafc79ea9ef87c187a56b411.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F132155_772dbf44aafc79ea9ef87c187a56b411.jpg&h=49432ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n儘管有這種需求，但這家開發商仍然對他們的下一款遊戲絕對保密。但新的情報似乎表明，該作可能最終會在下周E3亮相。<br />\n<br />\n消息來自4chan，聲稱遊戲將於本週正式公佈，Rocksteady將在當地時間週日下午4點開始的微軟E3大會期間，首次放出遊戲片段。<br />\n<br />\n目前還不完全清楚預告內容是什麼，但可能是布萊尼亞克入侵地球，與超人展開戰鬥。遊戲畫面將展示飛行控制和新的戰鬥系統，超人將在地面和天空中與各種無人機對戰。<br />\n<br />\n同時，<a href=\"http://一個新的網站supermangame.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99supermangame.com&d=kdpm3TGC%2FPzajP3Vx6HhkKMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=71c039d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">一個新的網站supermangame.com</a>已經在準備中，但還尚未正式上線。預計本週晚些時候遊戲推出後，它會上線。"},{"pid":"1852735b41c7561612458ef8da7cc14952d4c07b","tid":689418,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"超人發揮空間唔似蝙蝠俠咁大"},{"pid":"d5c7dfa524d557c24ac216c4f6ee6851f56b458c","tid":689418,"uid":108575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1852735b41c7561612458ef8da7cc14952d4c07b","tid":689418,"uid":48791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"超人發揮空間唔似蝙蝠俠咁大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"變無雙"},{"pid":"fa0d36d9b5e6f348ee7d8599b11ef762682d84f5","tid":689418,"uid":173852,"like":6,"di